    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that. but if a system is basically designed to let the most powerful countries ignore rules whenever they want, doesnt that make its claim to \"international peace\" kind of a joke? wouldn't a historian say the whole institution is just a way for a few countries to maintain their own dominance under the guise of global law?",
